Use Sonner for All Notifications

Always use Sonner for all application notifications and alerts
Do not use Toast or any other notification libraries in new code
Migrate existing Toast implementations to Sonner when modifying related code

Sonner Implementation Guidelines


// Import Sonner
import { toast } from 'sonner';

// Basic success notification
toast.success('Operation completed successfully');

// Error notification
toast.error('An error occurred while processing your request');

// Info notification with custom duration
toast.info('Your session will expire soon', {
  duration: 5000
});